title: Kinda Confuzzled... ?
body:
Today I was in Melbourne at a gaming cafe, I opened league of legends boards and the Miscellaneous tab was gone? General Discussion was still there though... Everything looked updated, it's the same if i use my phone.. Also I had no notifications, however when I got home i did have notifications?

I came home today from my trip to Brisbane and the boards are still the same as what they were before i left. Can anyone explain this?

replies.body: Did you open the OCE version? Other regions look slightly different
yeah i think that was what happened :P i figured it out last night. Thanks though
